Title: Robo Wars
ShortDesc: Learn to equip% equip to fight% fight to defend. Defend the flag with your Battlebot in our Robowars.
LongDesc: Learn to equip% equip to fight% fight to defend. Defend the flag with your Battlebot in our Robowars.

Title: Siege
ShortDesc: Build the dreaded war machine of the ancient world% the catapult% aiming to destroy any other pitted against you.
LongDesc: In this event you'll use your creativity to design and build the dreaded war machine of the ancient world% the catapult% aiming to destroy any other pitted against you. So only if you have what it takes to take part in this Battle Royale% then get ready to lay SEIGE to your opponents.

Title: Tech Wars
ShortDesc: Intense competitions involving ethical hacking% aerospace and reverse engineering where you put your problem solving and debugging skills to the test!
LongDesc: Grab your fellow geeks and prepare for some intense competitions involving ethical hacking% aerospace and reverse engineering where you put your problem solving% debugging and other technical skills to the test! Tech Wars - be ready.

Title: Galactica
ShortDesc: A glimpse of the future% a race against time! Give the Jetsons a run for their money by reimagining your own utopian space settlement!
LongDesc: A glimpse of the future% a race against time! Give the Jetsons a run for their money by reimagining your own utopian space settlement!

Title: Gear Up
ShortDesc: Does the practical application of Physics intrigue you? Challenge your innovative guts and discover the hidden scientist inside you.
LongDesc: Does the practical application of Physics intrigue you? If yes% then here's your chance. Challenge your innovative guts and your mental skills by becoming a part of our Gear Up family% which might help you discover the hidden scientist inside you.

Title: Tour De Mind
ShortDesc: Do you think you have the skills to be a detective? Does deciphering code get your blood flowing? Three days of deciphers% RGMs and fun!
LongDesc: Do you think you have the skills to be a detective? Does deciphering code get your blood flowing? Then this is the event for you. Three days of deciphers% RGMs and fun!

Title: Math Gauge
ShortDesc: Be the smartest and stupidest with us and join Math Gauge% the most thrilling event of PSIFI% full of fun and real challenges!
LongDesc: Be the smartest and stupidest with us and join Math Gauge% the most thrilling event of PSIFI% full of fun and real challenges and reveal...

Title: Diagnosis Dilemma
ShortDesc: Teams will be tested on the basis of their medical knowledge and their perseverance under pressure and only those that are able to keep their cool and perform will be able to make it.
LongDesc: Get ready for a unique challenge in this year's PsFi: Diagnosis Dilemma; where teams will be tested on the basis of their medical knowledge and their perseverance under pressure and only those that are able to keep their cool and perform will be able to make it.

Title: Science Crime Busters
ShortDesc: Use your detective skills and forensic knowledge to eliminate the impossible and unravel the truth.
LongDesc: Use your detective skills and forensic knowledge to eliminate the impossible and unravel the truth.
